[I] Perl module XML-RegExp

[T] This package contains regular expressions for the following XML tokens:
[T] BaseChar, Ideographic, Letter, Digit, Extender, CombiningChar, NameChar,
[T] EntityRef, CharRef, Reference, Name, NmToken, and AttValue.

